column2: Hi miss, I think your clothes are cool.
How is your skin so soft like this?
It's because I'm a Clean Girl, so I use a lot of products to keep it like this :)
Cool, how can I be like that too?
To be as pretty as me, first you need to straighten your hair, change your avatar's skin to a beautiful one.
What's wrong with my skin color?
Clean Girls got light skin like mine, sis, that's the only way you can be a diva like me.
That's not true, my beauty is unique, and there's no such thing as beautiful skin or ugly skin, all colors are beautiful.
Sorry activist, I'ma block you, alright babe!!!
Is it possible to do that?
